- [ ] Fetch-skip/rate-limit behavior based on XP gain is implemented.
- [ ] Rank-only changes are ignored for fetch-skip decisions.
- [ ] Placeholder test coverage is replaced or supplemented.
- [ ] CI passes with Ruff, Black, and pytest.

